<h1>Chai Latte</h1>

contents of 2 bags of assam tea<br/>
1 tsp ground cinnamon<br/>
1/2 tsp ground ginger<br/>
1/4 tsp ground allspice<br/>
contents of 4 cardamom pods<br/>
2 cup water<br/>
1/4 cup brown sugar<br/>
2.5 cup milk<br/>

1. Combine tea, cinnamon, ginger, allspice, cardamom, and water in saucepan.

2. Bring to a boil, boil for five minutes.

3. Add sugar.

4. Add milk.

5. Return to a boil.

6. Remove from heat, strain.
